*You resume cleaning up the mess in the room while staying as quiet as possible.*
“I know you’re there! Don’t pretend like you’re not.”
*Sigh*
“Hi…old friend”
“Old friend?? HAHAHA. Oh man! That’s funny. Okay then, hey…FRIEND”
*You blush and don’t say anything. The silence is deafening.*
“You look good” *he winks*
*Your cheeks get even redder and you hurriedly finish mopping up the dirt and water*
Okay..umthanksniceseeingyou…BYE!
*You exit the room in world-record speed*
